---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
import Breadcrumbs from '../components/Breadcrumbs.astro';
import InquiryForm from '../components/InquiryForm.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Assess My Mineral Processing Project"
  description="Submit the ore type, target capacity, project stage and known test data for an initial mineral processing project review within one business day."
>
  <header class="page-hero">
    <div class="container">
      <Breadcrumbs items={[{ label: 'Assess My Project' }]} />
      <span class="eyebrow">Initial review at no charge</span>
      <h1>Assess My Project</h1>
      <p>
        You can send an imperfect project brief. Tell us what you are processing, what is already
        known and what is causing trouble. We will identify the likely route, missing information
        and the next practical step.
      </p>
    </div>
  </header>
  <section class="section assessment">
    <div class="container assessment-grid">
      <InquiryForm />
      <aside>
        <span class="eyebrow">What I look for first</span>
        <p class="reviewer-note">
          A useful first reply comes from the ore facts, not from pushing a machine model.
        </p>
        <ol>
          <li><strong>Ore type</strong><span>Alluvial or rock, clay level, visible heavy minerals and feed size.</span></li>
          <li><strong>Capacity</strong><span>Target TPH, working hours, water source and power condition.</span></li>
          <li><strong>Current bottleneck</strong><span>Where material is lost, blocked, too wet, too fine or not liberated.</span></li>
          <li><strong>Existing equipment</strong><span>What you already own, what must be reused and what site limits exist.</span></li>
        </ol>
        <p>
          After that, we reply with the missing questions, a likely process direction and whether
          testing or a more detailed scope is needed.
        </p>
      </aside>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .assessment {
    background: var(--paper-deep);
  }

  .assessment-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: minmax(0, 1fr) 300px;
    align-items: start;
    gap: 34px;
  }

  aside {
    padding: 28px;
    color: var(--white);
    background: var(--charcoal);
  }

  aside .eyebrow {
    color: var(--gold-light);
  }

  ol {
    margin: 8px 0 24px;
    padding: 0;
    list-style: none;
  }

  li {
    padding: 17px 0;
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.12);
  }

  li strong,
  li span {
    display: block;
  }

  li strong {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 1.2rem;
    text-transform: uppercase;
  }

  li span,
  aside p {
    color: rgba(255, 253, 248, 0.62);
    font-size: 0.78rem;
  }

  .reviewer-note {
    margin: 0 0 14px;
    color: rgba(255, 253, 248, 0.78);
    font-weight: 700;
  }

  @media (max-width: 900px) {
    .assessment-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
